metadata.description: From the biggest storylines to the funniest compilations, the Archie Comics Graphic Novel series has it all! These books give you the most bang for your buck -- and there are several new editions popping up every month! Be sure to stay tuned for the next awesome collection starring Archie, Jughead, Betty & Veronica and even Sabrina the Teenage Witch!
metadata.name: Archie Comics Graphic Novels
